title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Triquicornio

Halcondrilo cree que solo son Master Frown y Brock en un disfraz de burro tratando de arruinar las cosas, pero Unikitty y Perricornio están convencidos de que Triquicornio en un viejo miembro de la familia. Halcondrilo sigue sus instintos de guardaespaldas e intenta probar que Triquicornio es un impostor.

title: The Sunflower

title: Meet Cheetara

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs

The girls think they're experiencing deja vu but it's really just Mojo working his maniacal mischief.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Meet Lion-O

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain

When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: A Fragile Hope

Pero ¿será capaz de salvar a todos y conservar su empleo justo a tiempo?

description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: #DramaQueen

description: Gracias a la tarea de la clase de Economía Domestica, los estudiantes son emparejados y se les entrega un huevo para "cuidar" durante el fin de semana. Pero cuando la tragedia acontece huevo tras huevo, lo que debería ser una tarea fácil, ise convierte en una disparatada persecución!

title: Dunklecorn

Hawkodile thinks it's just Master Frown and Brock in a donkey costume, trying to ruin things as usual, but Unikitty and Puppycorn are convinced Donklecorn is an old family member. Hawk follows his bodyguard senses and tries to prove that Donklecorn is a fake, until finally the real Master Frown and Brock show up and ruin things, just as he suspected they would. He admits he was wrong about Uncle Donklecorn, but all is forgiven and the friends dance it out together.

title: El camino dorado

title: Un Nuevo Empleo

title: The Headsucker's Moxy/Equal Fights
description: The Headsucker's Moxy: There's a mysterious villain in town who's sucking pertinent information from the brains of powerful people and committing crimes. How do the girls trap this sucker before his next victim is drained?/Equal Fights: When the girls try to catch a local female villain, she tells them that as women they've got to stick together. It's up to the women of Townsville to teach our heroines the true meaning of equality.

title: The AB Bakugan Battle League!
description: With all the mayhem and destruction Haavik is causing, the Awesome Brawlers decide that a bit of Bakugan brawling is the perfect distraction to take their minds off all the trouble. With the help of some friends, they start the Awesome Brawler Bakugan Battle league!/ The Awesome Brawler's Bakugan Battle league rages on. Just as the semifinal round comes to a close, an uninvited guest crashes the party, bringing an alarming end to the battle league.

title: The Gauntlet Part 2
description: As Dr. Light and Suna turn the Robot Masters against each other, Mega Man defeats and unmasks his arch nemeses, Lord Obsidian, who turns out to be Sgt. Night in disguise, and finally learns the identity of Namagem, Mega Man's long lost twin brother!

title: Action Comedy
description: Rhyboflaven's local fictional superhero, Broccoli Punch, has an all-new, spectacular action stage show, but when Flonk masquerades as the star, the Warriors disguise themselves as broccoli bad guys to teach the imposter a lesson!

title: I Am Chair
description: During a stressful trip to the mall, Robin finds peace in a massage chair.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
Wednesday - Part 1
description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

title: Kitty y Halcon: Protectores de la Ley
description: Cuando el juguete favorito de Perricornio desaparece, Unikitty y Halcondrilo se unen para localizar al ladrón, ial estilo socios policías! Pero cuando las cosas se ponen difíciles y el caso no se resuelve, ya no es solo su sociedad la que está en juego, sino también su amistad.

title: Throwing Shade Part 1
description: Sgt. Night publicly criticizes Dr. Light's views on human & robot unity during a school assembly, invoking the ire of Fire Man and forcing Silicon City's newly minted hero, Mega Man, to intervene.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Iron & Stone
description: Cole and Young Wu attempt to free their friends, who have been taken captive by a tribe of Dragon Hunters. Meanwhile in Ninjago, Lloyd is reunited with some old friends who may prove valuable allies against Emperor Garmadon.

title: Haavik's Challenge/Storm Haavik's Tower
description: Haavik's Challenge: Haavik has crashed the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan League, and challenges the Awesome Brawlers in a battle league of his own!/ Storm Haavik's Tower: In order to keep Earth and Vestroia safe and rescue Drago, the Awesome Brawlers agree to enter Haavik's Bakugan Battle League, and race toward Haavik's tower for the final showdown.
